Hermes Agent for digital-world.dev
==================================

This repository is a substantially adapted Traefik/digital-world.dev deployment variant inspired by:

  oliverhees/hermes-agent-oneshot-installer
  https://github.com/oliverhees/hermes-agent-oneshot-installer

The upstream project is MIT licensed. The original concept provided a one-shot Hermes Agent installer using Docker, Caddy, TLS and Basic Auth. This version changes the deployment model to an existing Docker/Traefik server environment, uses digital-world.dev paths, domains and labels, and adds operational scripts/docs for publishing under the digital-world.dev / Steve72HH GitHub namespace.

Hermes Agent itself is developed by Nous Research:

  https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent

This repository does not vendor Hermes Agent source code. It deploys the official container image by default:

  nousresearch/hermes-agent:latest
